title: U.S. warships sail near islands claimed by Beijing
text:
U.S. warships sail near islands claimed by Beijing 11:20am EDT - 01:06
Two U.S. Navy warships sailed near South China Sea islands claimed by China on Sunday, two U.S. officials told Reuters, in a move likely to anger Beijing as President Donald Trump seeks its continued cooperation on North Korea. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
